properties.name: Road Closed
properties.description: CO 14 Westbound / Eastbound Teds Place to Stove Prairie Road (Milemarker 121-106)Co 14 is closed between US 287 and Stove Prairie Road due to a wild fire. No through traffic between US 287 and Walden. Road closure began May 17th, 2012 at 12:00pm. Alternate route is local detours.
